A crowd of students from Northwest Prep Academy descended on a gas station in Memphis, Tennessee on Monday . 
 They began to yell and throw up gang signs and then attacked a man,  Orrden Williams Jr.Williams ended up covered in bruises because of the unprovoked attack, and his baby was also almost hit by the teens . 
 Police are investigating and have made one arrest in the case, 19-year-old Joe Brittman . 
 